window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Four astronauts left home to be the first humans on Mars. What didn't come back will haunt life on Earth forever. </p> <p>Follow the adventure as disaster triggers the greatest treasure hunt in history - spanning the globe and beyond. The prize is nothing short of humanity's very survival. </p> <p><i>Blue Hope</i> marks the final book in the Red Hope series, but it can also be enjoyed as a stand-alone adventure. </p>"; 
